cat << EOF
kradview is a viewer of images obtained for some different sources: X-ray, NMR
and all DICOM-compatible imaging devices. Its aim is to be a complete platform
for medical imaging and image processing. It has been developed during my work
on my Ph.D.; what is oriented by prof. Dr. Carlos Renato Zacharias
(IBILCE-UNESP/Brazil) and prof. Dr. Antonio Falcó Montesinos (Universidad
Cardenal Herrera-SEU/Spain).
EOF
